            "uri": "https://rigor-mortis.nmrc.org/users/simplenomad/statuses/112960089048753644",
            "url": "https://rigor-mortis.nmrc.org/@simplenomad/112960089048753644",
            "replies_count": 0,
            "reblogs_count": 0,
            "favourites_count": 0,
            "edited_at": null,
            "content": "<p><span class=\"h-card\"><a href=\"https://infosec.exchange/@scottwilson\" class=\"u-url mention\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">@<span>scottwilson</span></a></span> Not me personally, but in other blog posts I\u2019ve recommended checking reviews, use only local and well established companies that specialize in solar, and insist on handling any finances yourself (or simply pay cash like I did). Search my blog site for \u201csolar\u201d for the details if curious.</p><p>I still get door-to-door solar sales people who 1) don\u2019t seem to notice the \u201cno solicitors\u201d sign and 2) the roof is covered in panels. I simply tell them (and any other solicitors) to get off the property and remotely turn on the sprinklers via Home Assistant to encourage them to leave.</p>",
            "reblog": null,
            "account": {
                "id": "109396515235068420",
                "username": "simplenomad",
                "acct": "simplenomad@rigor-mortis.nmrc.org",
                "display_name": "Simple Nomad",
                "locked": false,
                "bot": false,
                "discoverable": true,
                "indexable": false,
                "group": false,
                "created_at": "2022-11-23T00:00:00.000Z",
                "note": "<p>Long time <a href=\"https://rigor-mortis.nmrc.org/tags/Hacker\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>Hacker</span></a> type. <a href=\"https://rigor-mortis.nmrc.org/tags/Hippie\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>Hippie</span></a> and I care about the <a href=\"https://rigor-mortis.nmrc.org/tags/planet\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>planet</span></a>, ask me about <a href=\"https://rigor-mortis.nmrc.org/tags/solarpower\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>solarpower</span></a> and <a href=\"https://rigor-mortis.nmrc.org/tags/EV\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>EV</span></a>.</p><p>#\u2029RemoteWork since 1999, you know, since last century.</p><p>Been here since April 2022 and on this instance since Nov 2022.\u2029</p><p>Work is :gitlab: <a href=\"https://rigor-mortis.nmrc.org/tags/GitLab\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>GitLab</span></a>. Former ghost hunter and storm chaser. Survivor of <a href=\"https://rigor-mortis.nmrc.org/tags/cancer\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>cancer</span></a> and a <a href=\"https://rigor-mortis.nmrc.org/tags/widower\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>widower</span></a>. Links in the About. He/Him.</p><p><a href=\"https://rigor-mortis.nmrc.org/tags/Infosec\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>Infosec</span></a> <a href=\"https://rigor-mortis.nmrc.org/tags/hacker\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>hacker</span></a></p>",
